{"tid":2037244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国強推港版國安法   川普:本週將提制裁方案","createTime":"2020-05-27T01:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:35:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d906fd82113a8a1cf5527637399a0d25a93ed1f4","tid":2037244,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/img.globalnewstv.com.tw/uploads/2020/05/20200527085019_30.jpg?resize=1045%2C570\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fimg.globalnewstv.com.tw%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F20200527085019_30.jpg%3Fresize%3D1045%252C570&h=4bc9c65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國強推香港版國安法，香港民眾返回街頭遊行抗議，國際也再度關注香港問題。根據彭博報導，美國川普政府正在考慮對中國的制裁方案，而川普26日被媒體問到時，表示這個問題很重要，但他現在無法回答，因為還在討論中，但強調本週結束前會提出「非常強而有力」的應對方案。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮國家顧問歐布萊恩之前接受節目專訪時也表示，如果中國強推香港版國安法，將可能導致美國制裁，並危及香港金融中心的地位。(照片來源: Joshua Wong 黃之鋒 推特)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://globalnewstv.com.tw/202005/107960/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglobalnewstv.com.tw%2F202005%2F107960%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8Uy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a7b40fec\" target=\"_blank\">http://globalnewstv.com.tw/202005/107960/</a>"},{"pid":"33e7f5026d06caa6cad84a8fd9e2cc6e972d644e","tid":2037244,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}